Use pure CSS for all styling in this project. Follow these guidelines:
- Use CSS variables (defined in :root) for colors and common values
- Keep styles in src/styles.css
- Use semantic class names (e.g., page-container, nav-link)
- Follow the existing organization (Layout, Typography, Components)
- Maintain consistent spacing using rem units
- Use CSS transitions for interactive elements